text: Pavel Sokol (born 30 June 1969) is a Czech rower. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Uherské Hradiště
